        Build-A-Bear donates 5,000 bears to Red Cross
    


By Lisa Brown
St. Louis Post-Dispatch











Lisa Brown


























Jul 20, 2017

 (…)












































Buy Now


FILE PHOTO: A Build-A-Bear Workshop retail store at West County Mall in Des Peres on November 17, 2016. (Photo by Michael Thomas)


Michael Thomas


































































