FREE SHIPPING!
	Free FedEx - SmartPost shipping applies to all orders over $40 shipping to U.S. addresses only. The discount code SHIPFREE40 is applied automatically to orders. For all other shipping rates see www.buildabear.com/ShippingInformation. Offer does not apply to previous orders. Free FedEx - SmartPost shipping does not include Canada and International orders.












Our Products

Whether you're inspired to create a silly, sassy, superhero, a motorcycle-riding princess, or any of the gazillion other ideas that flow when you stop, listen and let yourself play again, every Build-A-Bear made is one of a kind. 
Choose from more than 30 animals to make. Select a heart, whisper a wish and seal it with a kiss! Whatever you imagine your furry friend to be, we'll help you choose outfits, accessories, even scents and sounds, to bring your fantasy to life. When you walk out hand-in-paw with your new best friend the real adventure is about to begin…and we can't wait to make friends with you over and over again!

 














































































