Build a Bear is GREAT!
10/19/2005













5

Nadia L.


                        I love this store for many reasons, not just because I have received cute gifts from friends from here but because it is a wonderful place to get a fun and personal gift for a family friend, boyfriend, girlfriend, etc. 

If you aren't familiar with Build a Bear's, it is a teddy bear factory where you can choose an animal (they have bears, frogs, monkeys, etc) and then you get to stuff it with fluff and even put a little heart in it. Then you get to name your little friend, choose clothes for him/her and then take him/her back in a little carboard house. 

It is a wonderful place that kids and adults both love and I think it's just a fun place to go. 
                        more



